2011-15-10  Antonello Provenzano  <antonello@deveel.com>
	* AuthResult.cs: Added property Context to keep a reference
	on the authentication context
	* IAuthenticator.cs: 
		- added method CollectData to populate the authentication 
		data dictionary with additional elements
		- introduced method EndContext to dispose an eventually
		created context at the moment of authentication
	* ServiceConnector.cs: authentication logic added to the
	explicit implementation of Connect

2011-03-01  Antonello Provenzano  <antonello@deveel.com>
	* AuthResult.cs: added property 'OutputData' to provide
	authorization processors a patch to output data in the
	stream.

﻿2011-27-09  Antonello Provenzano  <antonello@deveel.com>
	* AuthenticationCode.cs: enumeration added to expose well-
	known and reserved authentication codes
	* AuthResult.cs:
		- introduced overloaded constructors for
		accepting AuthenticationCode enumeration;
		- removed boolean argument 'success'
	* AuthRequest.cs: added overloaded constructor that allows
	the specification of a dictionary of authenticatin metadata

2011-09-07  Antonello Provenzano  <antonello@deveel.com>
	* IAuthenticator.cs: removed method IsProtocolSupported
	* AuthRequest.cs: data dictionary modified to accept the
	AuthObject value.

2011-07-25  Antonello Provenzano  <antonello@deveel.com>
	* IAuthenticator.cs: 
		- introduced argument to method Authenticate for indicating 
		the authentication end-point
		- added property Mechanism to indicate esplicitely the
		authentication mechanism used by the implementations of
		the interface
		- method IsProtocolSupported added to check if the protocol
		is supported by the authentication mechanism